Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He belongs to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a single thing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.75,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Calmato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. So that's Touka's kagune...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad, Miss Kirishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine, me taking this much damage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from someone whose\Nkagune is well-matched to mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd get\Nto see you like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the passion from that earlier time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is being reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me dress the area around Kaneki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,using your organs as trimmings!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an unexpected {\i1}hors d'oeuvre!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Miss Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely not what I'd hoped for...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but tactically...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go!\NLet me go! Let me go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite enough--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have this, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This will take...\Nan awful long time... to heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneki... for heaven's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one... bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat your own flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you filthy gourmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on... I'm coming to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,help you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Touka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows about\Nboth you and Kaneki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let a woman this dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Touka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! She's like...\NHide is to me, or Yoriko is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that was Yoriko\Nup there and not Miss Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to kill Yoriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get rid of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure that doesn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I... pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:26.70,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Tell me, oh tell me, the way it works
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:33.92,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Who is that inside of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:41.14,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Here in this broken-down,\Nbroken-down world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:47.85,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,you laugh, without seeing a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:08.66,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,I'm just so damaged,\NI hold my breath and freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:12.25,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Breakable, unbreakable;\Nshakable, unshakable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.96,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,When I found you, it shook me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:22.97,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,In this twisted world, I'm gradually\Ngrowing transparent and vanishing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:30.10,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Don't look for me; don't look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:33.60,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,I don't wish to hurt you in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:37.19,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,of someone else's imagining
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:41.61,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Remember who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Following the incident at
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--All right, that's perfect.\N--Good work.\N--the church, there were a number of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--We're still doing the daily prep, you know.\N--changes around Anteiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention the little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Nishio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've got your usual\Nmaggot-infested look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nishio came to work at Anteiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For Miss Kimi's sake, as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should\Ntake any more human lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With the food that we gather here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you can live a relatively\Nguilt-free life as a ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we make sure to exact a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be your\Nlabor here at Anteiku, Nishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I have to say, Mr. Nishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I look at you, the less\Nyou mesh with Anteiku's formalness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kick you out of here.\NWe're still just doing the daily prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, what made\Nyou start working at Anteiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. I have my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're after Touka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Like I'd want that brainless girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Touka,\Nis she still not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Touka hadn't been at work since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,want to be with Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? All sorts\Nof things can happen in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I've got class!\NThanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault. With him not here,\NI have to be twice as together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what is Hinami\Nupset about, if I can ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't heard anything from him--\Nfrom my husband, in some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So now she insists on going to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Hinami's father right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are awfully quiet here today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this with you and get on out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very nice.\NYou really do do good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get her with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Would you mind not\Ncoming around here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see I've fallen into disfavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami... Ryoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be together again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if you\Nwould tell me something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When the hell did you\Nbecome a flunky of the humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was apparently mixed up in some\Ndangerous business in the 13th Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,once Hinami was born,\Nhe got out of that for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is a good man.\NTo Hinami and me, he really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't spoil Hinami, she'll\Nnever get the chance to be spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A box-carrier...\NWhat are doves doing here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it was worth\Nthe wait, wasn't it, Amon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Using small fry to catch the bottom feeders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, this one is a\Nbottom feeder in the truest sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mado, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason. What is the\N13th Ward's big fish doing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,swimming around in the 20th Ward?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we hear it\Nstraight from his own mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,An S-rated... The 13th Ward's Jason...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami? It's Mom. Can you open up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami, your--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Dad! Why?!\NWhy can't I?! I hate you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Hinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't have raised my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You miss Dad, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Dad misses you, too, Hinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, if we go see\Nhim now, we'll be in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to always\Nmake you put up with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason! Jason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, I'll entertain you for two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I guess\NI didn't step in close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NYou can nail him with the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,quite easily breakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Amon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's up. Let's play again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mado?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, my quinque broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what use might we have for this scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom misses Dad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm. Mom, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. I won't cry\Nanymore. Thank you, Hinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait together until...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad comes to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason managed to get away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My quinque broke.\NThere's nothing we could have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we keep\Nsquashing them one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,another opportunity will come around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, we can use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, since I'm always\Nmaking you put up with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go get you a\Npresent to show you I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... It's about working tomorrow's shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Listen--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't... kill that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami and Mrs. Ryoko were fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were able to patch things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the two of them,\NI thought, families sure are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, the affection between
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,mother and child doesn't\Ncare about being human or ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be a surprise,\Nbut until my body ended up this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could all come to realize that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The relationship between\NMr. Nishio and Miss Kimi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,could serve as a guidepost for the way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,things between human\Nand ghoul could be, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have opened\Nmy big mouth back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,without knowing anything\Nabout you and Yoriko, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll let the manager know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Touka must have thought so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After the way she herself\Nhad been accepted. But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,if she had been rejected,\Nafter interacting with each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there'd be no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for Hide and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Big Sister okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she starts feeling better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, let's continue.\NHow do you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... That's "cloudburst."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cloudburst"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It means when it suddenly starts raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you being taught how to read?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all. Well, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, look! I learned\Nall of the kanji in this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You did? That's good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a new book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn even more\Nwords, so I can surprise Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Dad's birthday\Nis coming up soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to give him a book as a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, why don't we go to the bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're in for a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! It's starting to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! Oh, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called a cloudburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When it suddenly starts\Nraining, it's called a cloudburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaneki is well informed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! I wonder if Dad knows, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask him sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I know something Dad doesn't\Nknow, I'm pretty amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's come over you, Hinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since\NI've gone out with you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, on, Hinami, you're getting wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we going to one other place? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Dad is somewhere nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to get us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Hinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dad's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that smell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice rain, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't want it\Nraining any harder than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to\Nhear your death throes, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a moment of your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Fueguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinami, run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. You head on\Nback to Anteiku ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay with you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusaba! Your Q-bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be\Nmother-daughter love? It makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody... Somebody...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother... Big Sister...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:18.58,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Though the city sleeps,\Nits buildings are always
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:20.96,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,under construction
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:23.34,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Urban planning carries on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:28.17,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Its belt lines morphing, snakes interlocking,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:33.01,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,stirring up endorphins,\Nand off you go, go, go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:37.68,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Souls ascend up into the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:42.36,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Their procession and\Ntheir faith both resembling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:51.95,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,an aberrant riddle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:58.33,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Our as-yet-empty tomorrows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:02.04,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,are an all but black shade of gray
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:08.01,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Without any possibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:11.72,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,an all but black shade of gray
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:18.22,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Ah, tonight, you're the one I want
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:21.27,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Saints
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:27.82,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Ah, I want you to signal the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.32,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Saints
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:35.12,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Saints
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.83,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Saints
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Nishiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.25,0:23:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to both wear these?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These are bangles. They're a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing. Is she\Nseriously going for a "pair" look?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}is {\i0}a present and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, these bangles are like horse crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Horse crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, no, Kimi... I meant, you know,\Nthe {\i1}good{\i0} kind of horse crap--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:24.98,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Next time: 'Captivity'"
